    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157000/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1762943257\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157000/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1762943257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157000/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1762943257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Pinevale Settlements》是一款融合生产与防御的殖民地建造模拟游戏。由小到大，收集资源、建造建筑、自动化生产、研究科技，并在愈发强劲的袭击中维持殖民地的生存。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完整版将包含：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 建造 – 防御 – 扩张</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  - 创建从采集者到作坊的生产链</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  - 运用城墙、箭塔与巡逻队抵御袭击</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  - 通过研究使用新建筑与效率加成</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 动态进程与挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  - 在季节循环中降低风险，应对不断增强的威胁强度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  - 管理资源瓶颈，规划优先级与库存</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 管理你的殖民地并提升生活质量</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  - 平衡生产面板，追踪库存，升级建筑</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  - 规划劳动力分配</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 开始探索与扩张</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  - 发现新区域、生物群系与发展机遇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  - 做出风险与回报抉择：稳健生产还是快速增长？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从抢先体验到完整版的路线图：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 新地图、生物群系与游戏模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 拓展科技树，新增建筑与防御类型</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 生活质量改进、生产平衡与性能优化</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们，书写你的定居点故事，让 Pinevale 持续生机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
